    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Get ready for an all-new RETRO style gaming experience!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176510/extras/1d635a3617e9858472ea2729bb2d1d60.avif?t=1761098521\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176510/extras_big/1d635a3617e9858472ea2729bb2d1d60.webp?t=1761098521 width=1560 height=504 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Jrago The Demon Hunter is an indie METROIDVANIA style 2D Platforming Action-Adventure Role Playing Game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">The world is overcome in darkness, and you are a hunter named Jrago on a quest to slay the demons and bring back the light!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176510/extras/d7d09b6910b039cad0fab0ea76eaba3f.avif?t=1761098521\" width=400 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Featuring an original soundtrack by &quot;Jrago&quot; the band of the same name, and a whole host of unlockable weapons, armor, magic spells, and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176510/extras/08620245e8d0b1543fc8849daf35be27.avif?t=1761098521\" width=126 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">30-40 Hours of Gameplay!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">51 Unlockable achievements!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Classic blue-squared mapping system!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">An expansive world divided up into 10 Chapters and 26 Boss fights!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">This is the first game developed by Jrago Studios, a solo indie developer based in USA.</p>",
